Explore two unique worlds as your favorite TRANSFORMERS characters
from TRANSFORMERS: Age of Extinction and Cybertron universes!

- Change Form Anytime: Effortlessly switch between robot and vehicle
form!
- Beyond the Movie: Weave your way through Earth and Cybertron
universes in an unforgettable battle to secure the Dark Spark.
- Epic Multiplayer Battles: Expanded four-player co-op online
escalation mode with new upgradeable defenses and challenging Power
Foes!

allowing players to unlock rewards that will aid progression in both
modes!
